00:49:35,650 --> 00:49:36,650
What's up?

609
00:49:44,100 --> 00:49:45,200
Hi, buddy.

610
00:49:45,700 --> 00:49:47,250
You like that?

611
00:49:47,500 --> 00:49:49,450
Toot-toot-toot-toot-toot

612
00:49:49,450 --> 00:49:50,550
You like that?

613
00:49:52,950 --> 00:49:53,850
Boo.

614
00:49:56,550 --> 00:49:57,450
Gotcha.

