00:49:59,000 --> 00:50:02,000
Ho!
Ho!
Ho!

616
00:50:04,200 --> 00:50:06,650
Hey! Hey, kid,
you took my fish!

617
00:50:08,800 --> 00:50:09,100
Yeah!

618
00:50:09,500 --> 00:50:10,000
Whoo!

619
00:50:10,200 --> 00:50:11,000
All right!

620
00:50:11,900 --> 00:50:13,250
I get your chocolate, buddy.

621
00:50:32,400 --> 00:50:33,600
What's the matter?

622
00:50:35,000 --> 00:50:36,900
What are you making
that awful noise for?

623
00:50:36,900 --> 00:50:39,600
[crying]

624
00:51:17,400 --> 00:51:18,500
Whoo!

625
00:51:21,200 --> 00:51:24,000
- What you got there?
- It's a toy I made for Willy.

626
00:51:29,350 --> 00:51:31,000
Big slap!

627
00:51:31,000 --> 00:51:33,450
One more!
Big slap, Willie!

628
00:51:34,000 --> 00:51:35,250
One more, buddy.

629
00:51:36,270 --> 00:51:37,000
Come on, Willy!

630
00:51:37,300 --> 00:51:39,700
Big circle, buddy, big circle!

631
00:51:39,700 --> 00:51:40,750
Big circle!

632
00:51:41,150 --> 00:51:43,000
Big circles, buddy.
Big circles!

633
00:51:54,150 --> 00:51:55,700
Come here, boy!

634
00:51:55,800 --> 00:51:57,000
Come on!

635
00:52:02,100 --> 00:52:04,850
Come on, boy.
Here we go.

636
00:52:15,000 --> 00:52:16,510
Whoo! Yeah!

637
00:52:17,700 --> 00:52:19,500
All right!

638
00:52:31,500 --> 00:52:35,000
There you go.
There you go.

