Yeah, well,
my mom's a pain.

753
00:59:43,430 --> 00:59:45,250
Couldn't take
care of me.

754
00:59:45,250 --> 00:59:47,250
Couldn't even take
care of herself.

755
00:59:47,450 --> 00:59:50,000
I haven't seen her
since I was a little kid.

756
00:59:50,000 --> 00:59:53,350
But, you know, I still miss her.

757
00:59:54,000 --> 00:59:56,600
Greenwoods, they're OK.

758
00:59:56,600 --> 00:59:58,450
They're OK.

